# Phase 2 — Recursive Portfolio Chatbot (Showcase 1)
#
# MOCK MODE (no services needed):
# - Leave all below commented out; the agent uses a local corpus and heuristic grader.
#
# REAL MODE (production setup):
# - Set DATABASE_URL (Neon pgvector)
# - Optionally add OpenAI/Anthropic/GitHub keys to enable real embeddings + streaming LLMs

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# DATABASE: Neon Postgres with pgvector
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Get this from neon.tech dashboard > Project > Connection > Pooled Connection
# Step-by-step: https://neon.tech/docs/connect/psycopg2
#
# DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:hash@ep-xxxxxx.neon.tech/portfolio?sslmode=require

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# EMBEDDINGS: OpenAI (text-embedding-3-small)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Used to embed query + corpus chunks for vector search.
# Get from https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# Cost: ~$0.02 per 1M tokens (negligible for this corpus)
#
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-proj-...

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# GENERATION: Anthropic Claude Sonnet
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Final answer stream from the grader's retrieved context.
# Get from https://console.anthropic.com/
#
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# OPTIONAL: OpenWeather API (Showcase 4 — live weather in playground)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Used by the playground get_weather tool.
# Without this key, weather falls back to canned London mock data.
# Free tier at https://openweathermap.org/api — "Current Weather Data"
#
# OPENWEATHERMAP_API_KEY=...

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# OPTIONAL: GitHub API (higher rate limits, seeding live activity)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_...

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# VERCEL BLOB: Showcase 2 PDF report storage
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Required in production. The SSE invocation that runs the research
# pipeline and the GET /api/research-pdf invocation are different
# serverless functions on Vercel — reports must live in shared
# storage so the download survives the handoff.
#
# Provision via Vercel dashboard → Storage → Create → Blob.
# BLOB_READ_WRITE_TOKEN is auto-injected when you link the store and
# is the only var the app reads — the canonical URL is discovered via
# the @vercel/blob head() SDK call, so no separate hostname is needed.
# Without this token, research-store falls back to an in-memory Map
# (works for `npm run dev` only — breaks on serverless).
#
# BLOB_READ_WRITE_TOKEN=vercel_blob_rw_...
